<h2 id="guidelines">Guidelines</h2>
<h3 id="title">Radio, checkbox, or select?</h3>
<p>There's many uses cases where a single checkbox works very well and other use cases where 50 checkboxes makes sense too. If only one of the options can be selected, use radio or select.</p>
<h3 id="a11y">Accessibility</h3>
<p>Like other input elements, be sure to use <code>for</code> and <code>id</code>.</p>
